2010年6月27日，'''[[冰島|冰島]]'''容許[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]的法律生效<ref>{{Cite web|author=Dwyer Arce|url=http://jurist.org/paperchase/2010/06/iceland-parliament-approves-same-sex-marriage-legislation.php|title=Iceland parliament approves same-sex marriage legislation|date=June 11, 2010|publisher=JURIST - Paper Chase|accessdate=2011-07-01|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919173428/http://jurist.org/paperchase/2010/06/iceland-parliament-approves-same-sex-marriage-legislation.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年6月11日，[[冰島國會|冰島國會]]在無人反對下通過性別中立婚姻法，而且公眾非常支持此法案<ref name="icenews1">{{cite web |url=http://www.icenews.is/index.php/2010/06/11/iceland-parliament-votes-for-gay-marriage/ |title=Iceland parliament votes for gay marriage |publisher=Icenews.is |date=2010-06-13 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2016-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128181759/http://www.icenews.is/2010/06/11/iceland-parliament-votes-for-gay-marriage/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。冰島成為全球第九個全國性給予同性註冊結婚的國家。

== 註冊伴侶 ==
1996年冰岛容許同性伴侶的[[註冊伴侶|註冊伴侶]]關系<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.france.qrd.org/texts/partnership/is/iceland-bill.html |title=Iceland : Recognized partnership law, 1996 |publisher=France.qrd.org |date=1996-07-01 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112010241/http://www.france.qrd.org/texts/partnership/is/iceland-bill.html |archive-date=2016-01-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。當性別中立婚姻法通過後，註冊伴侶就被取消。

註冊伴侶只適用於同性伴侶，給予等同[[婚姻|婚姻]]的保護、責任及福利。一名已註冊的伴侶能領養另一伴侶的小孩，除非小孩是來自外國。冰岛各黨派均支持註冊伴侶，只有一名保守派的獨立黨的議員反對。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/42.html#Iceland |title=Partnership Law In Iceland |publisher=France.qrd.org |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112010241/http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/42.html#Iceland |archive-date=2016-01-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/43.html#Iceland1 |title=A Victory For Icelandic Lesbians And Gays |publisher=France.qrd.org |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121194114/http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/43.html#Iceland1 |archive-date=2015-11-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/43.html#Iceland2 |title=Details Of The Icelandic Partnership Law |publisher=France.qrd.org |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121194114/http://www.france.qrd.org/assocs/ilga/euroletter/43.html#Iceland2 |archive-date=2015-11-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2006年6月2日，國會在無人反對下，通過給予同性伴侶等同異性伴侶在領養、養育及協助懷孕治療方面權益的法律。2006年6月27日法案正式生效。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ilga-europe.org/home/guide/country_by_country/iceland/important_improvements_in_gay_and_lesbian_rights_in_iceland |title=Important Improvements in Gay and Lesbian Rights in Iceland |publisher=Ilga-europe.org |date=2006-06-12 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227180052/http://www.ilga-europe.org/home/guide/country_by_country/iceland/important_improvements_in_gay_and_lesbian_rights_in_iceland |archivedate=2012-02-27 }}</ref>

2008年6月27日，新修改的法案容許[[冰岛國教會|冰岛國教會]]及其他宗教團體祝福同性註冊伴侶。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.icelandreview.com/icelandreview/daily_news/?cat_id=16539&ew_0_a_id=308516 |title=First Lesbian Couple in Iceland “Marries” in Church |publisher=Icelandreview.com |date=2005-12-06 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128181801/http://icelandreview.com/news/2008/07/02/first-lesbian-couple-iceland-marries-church |archive-date=2016-01-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

參與註冊伴侶的知名人士有前任女總理[[約翰娜·西于爾扎多蒂|約翰娜·西于爾扎多蒂]]及她的女伴侶。<ref name="CVMinistry">{{citation | title = Prime Minister of Iceland Jóhanna Sigurðardóttir | url = http://eng.forsaetisraduneyti.is/minister/cv | publisher = Prime Minister's Office | accessdate = 2 February 2009 | archive-date = 2017-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171018051454/https://eng.forsaetisraduneyti.is/minister/cv | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="time">{{Cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1875032,00.html|title=Iceland Picks the World's First Openly Gay PM|first=Jonas|last=Moody|publisher=[[Time_(Magazine)|Time]]|date=2009-01-30|accessdate=2009-01-31|archive-date=2010-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100519113022/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1875032,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年6月27日，她們的註冊伴侶關係轉變為婚姻關係。<ref>{{cite web |author=Peter Lloyd |url=http://news.pinkpaper.com/NewsStory.aspx?id=3298 |title=Iceland's Prime Minister marries long-term partner |publisher=News.pinkpaper.com |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305091530/http://news.pinkpaper.com/NewsStory.aspx?id=3298 |archivedate=2012-03-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2010/06/28/icelandic-pm-weds-as-gay-marriage-legislation-comes-into-effect/ |title=Icelandic PM weds as gay marriage legislation comes into effect |publisher=Pinknews.co.uk |date=2010-06-28 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2016-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160125141357/http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2010/06/28/icelandic-pm-weds-as-gay-marriage-legislation-comes-into-effect/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 同性婚姻 ==
2009年4月大選中勝出的冰岛政府宣佈將會引入性別中立婚姻法案。2009年5月19日，[[社會民主聯盟|社會民主聯盟]]及左翼綠色運動聯合政府宣佈會採納「單一婚姻法案」。雖然沒有指明，但已暗示了法案會是性別中立的。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eng.forsaetisraduneyti.is/news-and-articles/nr/3730 |title=Government Coalition Platform of the Social Democratic Alliance and Left-Green Movement |publisher=Eng.forsaetisraduneyti.is |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2010-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609042119/http://eng.forsaetisraduneyti.is/news-and-articles/nr/3730 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gayice.is/articles/gay-life/292-iceland-homosexuality-and-the-law |title=Iceland: Homosexuality and the Law |publisher=Gayice.is |date=2009-07-30 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2009-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090818170929/http://www.gayice.is/articles/gay-life/292-iceland-homosexuality-and-the-law |dead-url=no }}</ref>反對黨[[冰岛進步黨|冰岛進步黨]]亦支持性別中立婚姻法案。<ref>{{is icon}} [http://www.samtokin78.is/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=5107:framsoknarflokkurinn-sendir-fra-ser-alyktun-um-hjonabandsloeggjoefina&catid=1:latest&Itemid=26 Framsóknarflokkurinn sendir frá sér ályktun um hjónabandslöggjöfina] {{Wayback|url=http://www.samtokin78.is/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=5107:framsoknarflokkurinn-sendir-fra-ser-alyktun-um-hjonabandsloeggjoefina&catid=1:latest&Itemid=26 |date=20141011070955 }}</ref>

2009年11月18日，司法及人權部長確認冰岛政府正在推行包括同性及異性伴侶的「單一婚姻法案」。<ref>{{is icon}} [http://www.mbl.is/mm/frettir/innlent/2009/11/18/unnid_ad_setningu_einna_hjuskaparlaga/ Unnið að setningu einna hjúskaparlaga] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mbl.is/mm/frettir/innlent/2009/11/18/unnid_ad_setningu_einna_hjuskaparlaga/ |date=20100526092051 }}, mbl.is, 18 November 2009</ref>

2010年3月23日，政府公佈草案，取消註冊伴侶法及容許不論性別的伴侶皆可結婚。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://carnalnation.com/content/52178/4/iceland-likely-permit-gay-marriage-june |title=Iceland Likely to Permit Gay Marriage by June |publisher=Carnalnation.com |date=2010-06-27 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203060729/http://carnalnation.com/content/52178/4/iceland-likely-permit-gay-marriage-june |archivedate=2014-02-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sdgln.com/causes/2010/04/09/iceland-fine-tuning-marriage-equality-bill |title=Iceland is fine-tuning marriage-equality bill |publisher=Sdgln.com |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2015-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723105329/http://sdgln.com/causes/2010/04/09/iceland-fine-tuning-marriage-equality-bill |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年6月11日，冰島國會以49票贊成、0票反對、14票棄權和缺席通過性別中立婚姻法。<ref>{{is icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.althingi.is/dba-bin/ferill.pl?ltg=138&mnr=485|title=Hjúskaparlög, staðfest samvist o.fl. (ein hjúskaparlög)|date=2010-06-11|accessdate=2010-06-11|publisher=[[Alþingi|Alþingi]]|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713095948/http://www.althingi.is/dba-bin/ferill.pl?ltg=138&mnr=485|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="icenews1"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65A3V020100611 |title=Iceland passes gay marriage law in unanimous vote |publisher=Reuters.com |date=2010-06-11 |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2010-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010125452/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE65A3V020100611 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年6月27日正式生效。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.icenews.is/index.php/2010/06/28/new-gay-marriage-law-in-iceland-comes-into-force/ |title=New gay marriage law in Iceland comes into force |publisher=Icenews.is |date= |accessdate=2010-07-16 |archive-date=2010-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100630141012/http://www.icenews.is/index.php/2010/06/28/new-gay-marriage-law-in-iceland-comes-into-force/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

